title: Mastering Sex and Seduction with the LadyGang

description:
What’s better than one woman talking about sex? A foursome! On today’s show, Emily is joined by the amazing ladies of the LadyGang podcast, Keltie Knight, Jac Vanek, and Becca Tobin to talk all things sex, dating, and all the points in between!

You’ve become a first date master, but how do you get to that second one? How do you get on the same sex wavelength as your partner? Can you get back to a normal sex life after infidelity? Emily and the lovely LadyGang answer these sex and dating perplexities and more. Plus, the women cover phone obsession and relationship etiquette, their own sex lives, oral sex, marriage, and dating apps! Nothing is off limits with these ladies, so tune in for a great time!

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep this podcast free: Let's Get Checked, Adam and Eve, Womanizer 2Go, Intensity
